import { Text, View, Image, ScrollView } from 'react-native';
import { setting } from '../style/style.js';

export default () => {
  return (
    <ScrollView>
      <View style={setting.background}></View>
      <View style={setting.container}>
        <View style={setting.profile}>
          <Image
            style={setting.profilePicture}
            source={require('../assets/sprout.svg')}
          />
          <Text style={setting.name}>Bob Smith</Text>
        </View>
        <View style={setting.content}>
          <View style={setting.main}>
            <Text>hello world</Text>
          </View>
          <View style={setting.wrapper}>
            <View style={setting.content1}>
              <Text>hello world</Text>
            </View>
            <View style={setting.content2}>
              <Text>hello world</Text>
            </View>
          </View>
          <View style={setting.wrapper}>
            <View style={setting.content2}>
              <Text>hello world</Text>
            </View>
            <View style={setting.content2}>
              <Text>hello world</Text>
            </View>
          </View>
          <View style={setting.spacer} />
        </View>
      </View>
    </ScrollView>
  );
}
